        "name": "Test samples Gradation 3 criteria",
        "description": "N=11 constructs from production lot, assembled by trained technicians per ASTM F1717. Samples distributed across two independent laboratories. Lot traceability confirmed. No outliers excluded without documented justification."
      },
      "rationale": "Eleven non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs assembled from a single certified production lot (DePuy Synthes Expedium 5.5 mm rod, 7.5 mm non-cannulated screw). Constructs distributed 6 (Lab 1) and 5 (Lab 2). Technician qualification records on file. One outlier at Lab 2 (stiffness +2.3σ) retained after investigation confirmed no assembly error; inclusion documented. Sample size sufficient for Gradation 3 per ASME V&V 40 Table 4."
