      "rationale": "The validation activity (ASTM F1717 bench testing of N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs) directly matches the COU in device design, material, test standard, loading mode, and performance metrics. The same FEA model ensemble used for the COU prediction was used in the validation comparison. No extrapolation beyond the validated domain is required. Relevance matrix scores: geometry 3/3, material 3/3, loading 3/3, boundary conditions 3/3, QoI 3/3. Gradation 3 achieved."
